snippet.title: Cornucopia - Demo Coming Soon
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1681600/Cornucopia/
Cornucopia: A charming farming RPG sim featuring unique mechanics like a magnifying glass and compost system, as well as activities like logging, mushroom foraging, and animal breeding. Explore a bustling world, engage in combat, and participate in a variety of mini-games and festivals.
